<div class="mt-4 mb-4 p-5 bg-success text-white rounded">
    <h1>ERP.Reports.Api</h1>
    <p class="lead">Welcome to the Reports API! This API allows you to obtain various reports and statistical data.</p>
    <p><a href="/Swagger" class="btn btn-primary"><img width="50" height="50" src="~/Content/swagger.512.png" /> Swagger </a></p>
</div>

<div class="row px-4 py-4">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Swagger</h2>
        <p>To view and/or test the endpoints in detail, you can access our @Html.ActionLink("Swagger", "", "Swagger", new { area = "" }, new { target = "_blank" }).</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Help</h2>
        <p>You can also access the API's help area to obtain its @Html.ActionLink("Documentation", "Index", "Help", new { area = "" }, null).</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Donwload Reports</h2>
        <p>If you wish to download a specific report directly from your browser, please go to @Html.ActionLink("Download", "Index", "Download", new { area = ""}, null)  and review the endpoints.</p>
        
    </div>
</div>
